thread.title: Agnes
thread.title_full: ICoo Baby UK betygsatt av Agnes

author: Agnes
title: Agnes
text: They do not deal with customers in any level. One of the wheel came of during using, because the metal piece they provided was not strong enough. I asked for replacing the piece, never get one. Now the biggest problem is that the plastic is not strong enough in the back wheels and when I use the break they break out, now not many left, so the break not working properly. This stroller is not safe for any children and should not be sold .
